 for $49+$4 we felt it was a great value.FYI, to print your boarding passes at the business center is $7! No free wireless, but it is available for a fee, (I think $12). TV's are small, probably 17&quot;, and not many channels. Great free wireless at the airport, we really appreciated the free connection there.Oh, and Spamalot is great!	
